    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came here before the war, you know.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So they were like a poor family.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was like working in a factory, some jobs, still working.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my aunt was very nice, except she wanted me to go to a yeshiva.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wanted to please her in a lot of ways, but that I said, no.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I want to go to a regular school.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I ended up going to public school.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, within like one year, I graduated junior high school.",
