      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I didn't know that it was a difficult school to get into.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I insisted, no, I want to go there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I think he tried to humor me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I missed the entrance exam.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was a makeup exam.",
