      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he figured, OK, I'll let him swim.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he gave me a, a paper to go and take the makeup exam I took the makeup exam.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I must have done all right in the math, but I-- no way could I have done well on the English, because I didn't know English yet that well.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they graded it right away.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And maybe based on the fact that I-- that I'm just in the country about a year, they decided to accept me.",
