      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I got-- And how old were you when you did that, when you opened that business?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
