    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She's coming in from San Francisco.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm still in the dental equipment business.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're welcome.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there's very little, really, you can say.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you look at Bosnia-- and, you know, my area was like a little Bosnia.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's still happening 50 years later.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you look at Rwanda, you know, the Tutsis and the whatnot killing each other by the hundreds of thousands, by the millions.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'll-- if they don't know it themselves by now, I'll, I'll, I'll tell them that this was a dark chapter in our history.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and no way can Europe be the same after what happened, whether it's the religious community or the government communities.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I once spoke in a little town in Garrison, New York.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's mostly non-Jews there.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people were very receptive, very nice.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of them asked me a question, somehow trying to relate with the Vatican.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, well, I usually-- I don't like to get involved with-- but, I said to him, Poland was such a religious country.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Probably 95% or more of the Polish Catholics were very religious.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if at that time, the Vatican or the pope would have sent a message, at least to the Polish priests or the cardinals-- it didn't have to be in writing, even, if you are afraid to do it in writing because that could be dangerous-- to say to them, hey, you know, this is-- what's happening now is much more than, you know, than we normally allow with whatever antisemitism.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Unfortunately, Poland was an antisemitic country.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it wasn't just by themselves.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They learned it from others.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I would say thousands, maybe hundreds of thousands of Jews in Poland would have survived because the Germans, a lot of times, didn't know who was Jewish and who was not Jewish.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the local population made sure to point out, in case the Germans missed.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my wife, Betty.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her maiden name is Hellner, H-E-L-L-N-E-R.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She survived the war with her parents and brother.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was about three years old, so she doesn't remember that much.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do you remember from home?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't have any recollection at all of what transpired during the war.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only what my parents told me or my older brother has told me.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were very lucky in the fact that we had many Christian friends in the village who were-- couldn't help us outwardly, but they did help us indirectly by not giving us away and leaving food for us.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and of course, without my mother and father, I wouldn't have made it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't have any recollections.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's why I'm not as active as my husband is.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I find that it's very important to, to have a record of it.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's important that they have people like my husband that is doing it.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I'm sort of in the background.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This picture shows a group of children in Hebrew school, in kindergarten, and in the bottom row, sixth from the right, is my sister.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was taken before the war.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second picture shows my parents with a group of friends.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was also taken before the war.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother is middle of row, third from right.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father is bottom row, first from left.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this picture shows dedication of that Hebrew school where the children were photographed.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father is holding a dedication tray during the program.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the bottom is an enlargement of the picture from the kindergarten.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it shows my sister, second from right-- from left.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is a wedding picture of my oldest daughter, Paulette.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she's married to Alan Wolf.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're both doctors.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They met in medical school.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is my son, Kenneth Ginsburg.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he's married to Vicki [INAUDIBLE].",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She originally is from St.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Petersburg, Russia.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he now works in the finance industry.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is my youngest daughter, Suzanne Ginsburg.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She just spent three years in Japan doing research and teaching English.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And now she's back in the United States, in San Francisco.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And these are my grandchildren.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "On the bottom-- on the bottom is Zachary.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And next to him is Olivia.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And on top of Zachary is Ari.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And those are my daughter's three children.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And on the top left is Paulina and Sasha, and those are my son's children.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In 1993, I went back to my hometown.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And some of the surviving people collected some money, and we put up three monuments on three mass graves.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The top one has 400 men that were killed by the Einsatzgruppen in the beginning, when they first arrived in our town.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The middle one is the mass grave when they killed everybody in town.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that one contains 4,500 people, including, including my mother, my sister, my grandparents, and many relatives.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the bottom is a grave that contains some of the people that managed to run away from our town during the killing.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were tracked down later by Ukrainians and Germans.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they were buried in the woods.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that grave was left open for one month while they were capturing those people.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Even in our area, and in our town where the population was very unfriendly and collaborating with the Germans, there was still a few people that, in a way, risked their life to help Jews.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And this woman is one of them that saved a couple that now live in, in Florida.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "His name is Yakov Biber.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she was honored by Yad Vashem.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And her name is inscribed in the Washington Holocaust Museum and, and the-- on a special wall of righteous people.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    }
  ]
}